{"id":269508,"name":"","username":"elmuerte","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/elmuerte/{size}/27089_2.png","created_at":"2006-11-12T13:29:15.000Z","cooked":"<p>besides that afaik LBA2 doesnt actually use directdraw3d<br>\nso there is no hardware acceleration and thus no hardware features like aa</p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":13,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:50:23.513Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":10375,"topic_slug":"anti-aliasing-in-lba2","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":"staff","flair_url":"/uploads/default/original/3X/5/5/559743aa44a0676e04be9d54425231def12069c1.png","flair_bg_color":"","flair_color":"","flair_group_id":3,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":"","reply_to_user":{"id":2027,"username":"ContiX","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/contix/{size}/420_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"besides that... afaik LBA2 doesn't actually use directdraw3d\nso there is no hardware acceleration and thus no hardware features like aa","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":true,"admin":true,"staff":true,"user_id":1,"hidden":false,"trust_level":4,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/anti-aliasing-in-lba2/10375/4","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":269562,"name":null,"username":"ContiX","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/contix/{size}/420_2.png","created_at":"2006-11-12T22:16:08.000Z","cooked":"<p>Darnis there no way to up the game to use 16/32 bit or something?<br>\nOr rather, is there no way to force the game to use DirectDraw3d or something?</p>\n<p>As with my last few posts on things like this, this is one of those things that would probably need a redesign of the engine or something like that, right?</p>\n<p>Its not that I dont already love the game as it is - I just want to experiment a bit<img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":5,"post_type":1,"posts_count":13,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T17:50:25.514Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":1,"readers_count":0,"score":0.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":10375,"topic_slug":"anti-aliasing-in-lba2","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":2027,"username":"ContiX","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/contix/{size}/420_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Darn...is there no way to up the game to use 16/32 bit or something?\nOr rather, is there no way to force the game to use DirectDraw3d or something?\n \nAs with my last few posts on things like this, this is one of those things that would probably need a redesign of the engine or something like that, right...?\n \nIt's not that I don't already love the game as it is - I just want to experiment a bit...:)","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id